<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">    A[ServiceLoader.load] --> B[读取配置文件]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">    B --> C[META-INF/services/接口全限定名]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">    C --> D[解析实现类全限定名]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">    D --> E[通过反射加载类]</span></span>
