<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_2-3-具体实现步骤" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-3-具体实现步骤"><span>2.3 具体实现步骤</span></a></h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>配置文件</strong>：在<code v-pre>META-INF/services</code>目录下创建以接口全限定名为文件名的配置文件</li>
<li><strong>文件内容</strong>：在配置文件中写入实现类的全限定名（每行一个）</li>
<li><strong>加载机制</strong>：通过<code v-pre>ServiceLoader.load(接口.class)</code>加载所有实现</li>
<li><strong>延迟加载</strong>：只有在遍历时才会真正实例化对象</li>
</ol>
